    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Affordable entry with long-term potential.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Tingalpa offers some of the best value in Brisbane's broader inner east. Larger blocks, good connectivity and improving infrastructure have attracted a growing number of first-home buyers and investors looking for yield and growth.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand the buyer profile active in Tingalpa and how to position properties to appeal to them. Whether you are selling a family home or an investment property, I will build a campaign that finds the right buyer at the right price.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Tingalpa Creek runs through the suburb's green edge, providing a natural amenity that buyers from denser suburbs notice and appreciate. The suburb's relative affordability compared with Cannon Hill and Murarrie makes it an attractive entry point for first-home buyers and investors who have been priced out of the inner-east ring. Industrial uses near the Gateway Motorway have historically kept values lower, but residential pockets away from that boundary have seen steady capital growth as buyers look further east. Infrastructure upgrades along the Gateway corridor continue to improve connectivity and have strengthened the suburb's investment case.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Tingalpa Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Eastern Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Growth Potential</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong investor interest</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/murarrie" style="color:#c4912a;">Murarrie</a>, <a href="/suburbs/cannon-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Cannon Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/hemmant" style="color:#c4912a;">Hemmant</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

